{"tid":1754563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Sometimes people deserve to have their faith rewarded.","createTime":"2019-11-25T09:04:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T09:05:44.000Z","uid":89868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3e060a8605b2efd0cc8d05c1ffe4d5e51722196d","tid":1754563,"uid":89868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:04:39.000Z","msg":"我知道距離落實五大訴求，仲有好長一段路，而我地好多手足都犠牲左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我更加對咩階段性勝利反感，咁會令我諗返起5年前...<br />\n<br />\n但係，我希望咁多位唔好一味係到屌慶祝嘅人先。雖然話唔係見到希望先去堅持，而係堅持落去先會見到希望。但經過呢咁多個月，我諗有好多人都攰啦（包括我，我知我冇用）<br />\n<br />\n正如標題所講，人係需要見到有回報，知道自己嘅付出冇白費力氣，先會更加堅持信念落去。今日嘅選情，可唔可以當作小小嘅慰藉、鼓勵比我地嘅手足呢？<br />\n<br />\n最後，我地要繼續反抗，已經開始見到曙光架啦，那怕只係少少。香港人加油！香港人反抗！香港人報仇！"},{"pid":"22e485275cc07c148ea2bdd64f99ad3edd2a1e6e","tid":1754563,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:05:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">依家我哋區選贏咗，外國好關注我哋！<br />\n係咪連少少嘢都唔肯做呀？</span><br />\n<br />\n最新的tweets 一定響bot <br />\n總之<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> Retweet Like Reply </span></span>就得<br />\n㩒入👉 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=75fed991\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">/task</span></span> 攞任務<br />\n<br />\nSen. Marco Rubio<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1198773889112956928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1198773889112956928&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=d19822d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1198773889112956928&h=2dc87735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRubio